Detailed Description

AddrPointNames is a container that stores the data of a address point file, and have methods for adding these names to SSIs.

This class works in three steps. 1) The file with address point information is read from disc and stored the container. 2) Call storeSsiDistances with all candidate maps as argument. 3) Call addAddrPointNamesToMap with all maps used when calling storeSsiDistances.
